title: The Football League Show 30.08.2014 PDTV X264
description:
The Football League Show
Saturday 30th August 2014 

Highlights and analysis from the Football League, presented by Manish Bhasin. Readjusting to life back in the Championship, Fulham and Cardiff go head-to-head at Craven Cottage. Sheffield Wednesday entertain Stuart Pearce's Nottingham Forest as both clubs look to build on encouraging starts. Plus the best of the action from the Amex as Brighton meet Charlton. Ser. 5.
